# 🦠 COVID-19 Global Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview
An interactive Power BI dashboard analysing the global impact of COVID-19 using the **Our World in Data (OWID)** dataset. This project was completed as part of the **AnalystLab Africa Data Analytics Internship**.

---

## 📊 Dataset
| Detail | Info |
|---|---|
| Source | Our World in Data (OWID) |
| File | owid-covid-data.csv |
| Rows | 429,000+ |
| Columns Used | 12 (selected from 67) |
| Date Range | January 2020 – August 2024 |

---

## 🧹 Data Cleaning (Power Query)
- Removed 55 irrelevant columns, retaining 12 key fields
- Changed `date` column from Text to Date format
- Replaced null values in vaccination columns with 0
- Changed vaccination columns from Text to Whole Number type
- Filtered out aggregated rows (World, income groups) using continent field

---

## 📐 DAX Measures Created
| Measure | Formula |
|---|---|
| Total Cases | `SUM(total_cases)` |
| Total Deaths | `SUM(total_deaths)` |
| Death Rate | `DIVIDE([Total Deaths], [Total Cases], 0)` |
| Total Vaccinations | `SUM(total_vaccinations)` |
| Recovery Rate | `DIVIDE([Total Cases] - [Total Deaths], [Total Cases], 0)` |
| Total Countries | `DISTINCTCOUNT(location)` |

---

## 📈 Dashboard Features
- **5 KPI Cards** — Total Cases, Total Deaths, Death Rate, Total Vaccinations, Total Countries
- **5 Charts:**
  - Global COVID Cases Trend (Line Chart)
  - Daily New Cases (Line Chart)
  - Top 10 Countries by Total Cases (Bar Chart)
  - Vaccination Progress by Continent (Column Chart)
  - Total Deaths by Continent (Donut Chart)
- **2 Slicers** — Continent (Tile) and Date Range (Between)

---

## 🔍 Key Insights
1. **USA led globally** with the highest confirmed cases (~100bn cumulative)
2. **Omicron peak (early 2022)** recorded ~2bn daily new cases globally
3. **Global death rate: 1.12%** of all confirmed cases resulted in death
4. **Asia dominated vaccinations** with 4T+ doses administered
5. **Europe accounted for ~29%** of global deaths despite smaller population share
6. **255 countries/regions** tracked across the full pandemic timeline

---

## 🎨 Dashboard Design
- Background: Dark Navy `#0A0A2E`
- Accent Color: Bright Blue `#00B4D8`
- Tool: Microsoft Power BI Desktop

